par, an elementary X11 status bar
=================================

information
-----------
this is a more extreme version of the original par idea:
less dependencies, less memory usage, same features.

requirements
------------
a zig compiler (version 0.15.1 recommended) w/ std files
libxcb.so (no c headers required)

inspirations
------------
dmenu (https://tools.suckless.org/dmenu)
tint2 (https://gitlab.com/o9000/tint2)
lemonbar (https://github.com/LemonBoy/bar)
polybar (https://github.com/polybar/polybar)
